5 // значение opacity меньше 1.0 }); ``` Это установит прозрачность точкам в соответствии с установленным значением opacity - чем меньше значение опасити, тем меньше прозрачность точек."},{"prompt":"写一篇关于春天的诗","completion":"春之恋 翠绿的天空, 触摸世界的脉搏， 春风轻抚, 甜蜜乍泄。 阳光温暖地撒在大地， 万物复苏, 春回大地。 鸟儿在枝头欢唱， 花儿在丛中争艳。 萌芽探出新枝， 一片生机勃勃的景象。 春天的色彩, 繁花似锦， 点缀乾坤, 看那碧玉般的草地。 郁郁葱葱的桃花盛开, 红裳翠绿, 美得令人陶醉。 微风吹过, 落樱如雪， 满地金黄的蒲公英籽， 随风飘散, 寻找新生命的家园。 漫步其中, 脚踩黄金，绿蛋。 春天是自然的诗章, 醉人的景致, 四季之中的恋人。 悄悄萌生的爱情悄悄萌生, 在这美好中, 诉说着温柔的心弦。 只愿每一缕春风, 吹走心头的沧桑。 只愿每一片绿叶, 荡涤人间的浮躁。 只愿春天永驻, 在每个人的心田。 春天的故事, 仿若诗篇， 勾画出爱情的美丽牵绊。"},{"prompt":"describe Yuki as an attractive Japanese woman. Setting: Houston TX. Describe her revealing outfit. Show her suburban life. Yoga pants.","completion":"Yuki was a stunning Japanese woman who turned heads wherever she went. She had glossy, long black hair that cascaded down to her waist, and her almond-shaped eyes were big and bright, with thick lashes framing them perfectly. Her smooth, porcelain skin had a dewy glow to it, and her delicate features resembled those of a classic porcelain doll. On this hot and humid day in Houston, Yuki stepped out of her Toyota Prius, dressed in a revealing outfit that hugged her curves in all the right places. She was wearing a tight, white crop top that showed off her toned stomach, and a pair of figure-hugging yoga pants that accentuated her long legs. A pair of stylish black shades completed her look, adding a touch of glamor to her ensemble. Yuki lived in a cozy suburban house in Houston, where she led a simple yet fulfilling life. She enjoyed practicing yoga in her garden, surrounded by blooming flowers and chirping birds. In the afternoons, she would prepare healthy meals for herself, using fresh ingredients from the local farmer\'s market. On weekends, she would ride her bike around the neighborhood, enjoying the warm Texan sunshine and greeting her friendly neighbors. Despite her attractive looks and charming personality, Yuki never let her beauty define her. She wa